Class ReceiveTreasureTankerBehaviour

All Implemented Interfaces:
jade.util.leap.Serializable, Serializable
public class ReceiveTreasureTankerBehaviour extends jade.core.behaviours.SimpleBehaviour
This behaviour is automatically added to the Tanker agents. PROTOCOL_TANKER="ProtocolTanker"; An agent with the appropriate type call the method EmptyMyBackPack(TankerName) This method trigger a Request (TreasureType,Value) message The current behaviour wait for it and store the result in the agent
